B.JV=new A.iN("SOMETHING'S OFF","Gerald, we've noticed some... patterns.\n\nKeep watching. Trust your instincts.","The reports are getting stranger. Gerald isn't sure what's real anymore.","You stopped paying attention at the worst possible time.",B.DQ)
